      "writtenOn": "2026-01-23T05:05:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Could you provide comparative data or a technical breakdown regarding implementation complexity? Specifically, I would like to see a side-by-side comparison of integrating boost::awaitable with sdbusplus versus the lib-curl integration with sdbusplus to justify this architectural choice.",
      "revId": "c2873f82fb4e7c2b609a49ba290b5222fd934ff8",
